To sync remote directories or file
rsync -arv awx.yaml root@192.168.8.111:/home/
- use -i to perform a differential between directories
- use --progress to show progress when transfering large file
- use --include, --exclude to include and exclude file patterns when syncing

To delete file on remore dir 
rsync -arv awx.yaml --delete root@192.168.8.111:/home/
